class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Event\\RunEvent"
type: readonly class
summary: "Represents a domain event for a specific run execution, capturing sequence and turn metadata alongside a typed payload. Designed as a readonly value object to ensure immutability and safe propagation of run state changes within the domain layer."
